  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , the authors proposed a new algorithm for image segmentation in which segments are designated in the form of cuboids. The main idea is to use a greedy heuristic to recursively split a rectangular image into two rectangular halves with an optimal split line, orthogonal to one of the axes so that the value of distance metric is maximized.",
